$PROBLEM THEOPHYLLINE ORAL $INPUT ID AMT=DROP TIME DV BWT $DATA THEO $PRED DOSE = 320 KA = THETA(1) * EXP(ETA(1)) K = THETA(2) * EXP(ETA(2)) V = THETA(3) * EXP(ETA(3)) F = DOSE / V * KA / (KA - K) * (EXP(-K*TIME) - EXP(-KA*TIME)) IPRED= F Y = F + F * EPS(1) + EPS(2)
IF (ICALL.EQ.3) THEN WRITE (53,*) OMEGA(BLOCK) WRITE (54,*) SIGMA(BLOCK) ENDIF
